article.headline: Wright scores 16 as North Texas downs Wayland Baptist 80-38
article.description: — Atin Wright scored 16 points as North Texas beat Wayland Baptist 80-38 on Thursday.
article.linkText: Wright scores 16 as North Texas downs Wayland Baptist 80-38
article.story: DENTON, Texas -- — Atin Wright scored 16 points as North Texas beat Wayland Baptist 80-38 on Thursday. Wright also had three steals for the Mean Green (2-0). Latrell Jossell scored 12 points, going 4 of 10 (4 for 8 from 3-point range). The Pioneers were led by Jayvian Lawson, who recorded 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
